Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}岛田
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}曾根
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}高泽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.69,0:00:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沟口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山岸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.62,0:00:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以上被叫到的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果明天的补考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比之前的成绩还低的话就把你们的考卷复印了到处传阅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.80,0:00:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天放学后请教我数学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 不嫌弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.23,0:00:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 你是写了什么奇葩答案啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}起码我是抱着要解开题目的决心做答的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了让你更用功
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是传一下考卷比较好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是事不关己才说得那么轻松啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.71,0:00:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被到处传阅什么的 我死也不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.78,0:00:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也没什么事 没关系喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}帮大忙了 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是 要在哪里念书好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在图书馆又不能说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还是留在学校比较好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}来我家怎么样呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
