Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学 你刚刚叫我去你家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 在我家的话 就可以不受干扰专心念书了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在藤宫同学的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那真的是非常感激 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.40,0:03:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他的意思是不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.19,0:03:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去 我很想去藤宫同学家里看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办啊 将吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在藤宫同学的房间两人独处
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这怎么说都有点不妙吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你到底想做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}念…念书啦 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我呢 很向往邀请朋友来家里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你看看 她那天真无邪的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎…怎么办啊 将吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然将吾你也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你是男人吧 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说…说得也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感觉补考不加油不行了所以教我数学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}同班的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好期待啊 香织的家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是榻榻米吗 还是木地板呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好不容易可以跟藤宫同学两人独处的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.51,0:04:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话说回来 为什么连我也要跟来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感觉紧张起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 虽然说得有点晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然拜访会不会添麻烦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还真够晚的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我经常跟妈妈提起大家的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.91,0:04:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一定没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈妈 我带朋友回来了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}相当的慌张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.63,0:05:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是的 香织
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要来也提前说一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.39,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这位是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.64,0:05:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们是同班的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.31,0:05:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要烤蛋糕吗 大家喜欢蛋糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.44,0:05:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我最喜欢蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 不用费心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}烤蛋糕的话需要些时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.32,0:05:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去给大家端饮料来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等等再介绍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.54,0:05:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那上楼吧 我的房间在二楼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.67,0:05:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这里就是我的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是床耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.06,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好软喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}随便坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你们好歹给我犹豫一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊？ 为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.10,0:05:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不许看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是这样读日记的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 那日记丢掉的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是掉下来了没发现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.62,0:06:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为了能帮上长谷同学和沙希的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要加油的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.72,0:06:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}加油考个好分数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.18,0:06:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}山岸同学也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织 我可以看这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}将吾也说说她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为我没必要学习
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}话是这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天的补考
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和之前的小测验是同样的范围吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那就用那次的试卷来复习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}100分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.16,0:06:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好厉害 不愧是香织
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}于是你们多少分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.71,0:07:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真不该带你来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这道题…用这个公式就可以了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那这个也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.14,0:07:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 这个公式和这个公式是有关联的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.63,0:07:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是什么公式
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.57,0:07:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那这个公式记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊… 真不好说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一年级的时候学过的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我班里没教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.81,0:07:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学和沙希之前都是怎么活过来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也没造成什么不便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我什么时候才能回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.05,0:07:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我泡了茶 休息一下怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.43,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.51,0:07:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是买现成的 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}菠萝包
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}菠萝包我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妈妈 这几位是山岸同学 桐生同学和长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突然造访十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然…你就是长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个…我一直给藤宫同学添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是一直承蒙关照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我才应该这么说呢 一直有听香织说起你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}非常喜欢甜的煎蛋卷呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特别害怕数学呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我已经不知道听过多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真好啊 你被记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织说了很多长谷同学的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我就不打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}学习加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃完了 再加把劲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.49,0:09:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以借用一下厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 在楼梯拐角
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那先开始吧 沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃完了就困了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我就这么可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.17,0:09:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}越和长谷同学聊得来就越觉得桐生同学好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉抱歉 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你对藤宫同学做什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.68,0:10:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么都没做 谁会做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我不好 是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在开始让香织…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和桐生同学成为朋友的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那个 怎么回事山岸同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织貌似怕和桐生同学说话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我来想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.17,0:10:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希刚才听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}确实将吾看起来很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.25,0:10:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也从来不笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要么习惯要么放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}总之笑笑看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.35,0:10:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}别笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.85,0:10:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然只有习惯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那两个人说说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能去帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜欢学习吗 还是讨厌？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最近天气好的日子不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得是男方有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成为朋友作战中止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.77,0:11:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}应该说桐生同学不是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织不需要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.07,0:11:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我觉得不用做朋友也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在虽然还很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但我希望有一天能和桐生同学也成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因为 桐生同学是长谷同学的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以说你就当我是朋友好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管怎么说也都整天混在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也是时候明白了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}从今往后也多多关照了 桐生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.24,0:12:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃了晚饭再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用了 今天就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 我手机忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}房间也忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这边喔 沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.39,0:12:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}等会再看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 今天真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.36,0:12:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我往这边走 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.46,0:13:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}刚才藤宫的妈妈给你的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}写了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an9\fn腾祥铚谦钢笔简\blur0\bord0\c&H6A6A6A&}明天放学后请来一下公园 \N有话要跟你说 \N藤宫妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有话要说 应该是关于藤宫同学的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎么办 超级紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.86,0:13:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趁机说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我会保护藤宫同学的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你…你白痴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 虽然肯定是关于藤宫的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}恐怕就是二选一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}二选一？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于记忆的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}或是不要再纠缠她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你也一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不用这么紧张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对方只是个很温柔的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 虽然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自动贩卖机不就在那吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天没带钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 真是的 那就直接说借点钱好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可没把这当成借
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了好了 非常感谢你一直听我的抱怨和烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}几点开始来着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}时间没什么规定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨蛋 是补考啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:15:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对不起 今天有补考
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.48,0:15:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不不 我才是 突然叫你出来真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 请坐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}坐那么边上 话都说不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再坐近点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我留纸条给香织说今天稍微晚点回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 被人看到和这么年轻的男生在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大概会被认为是不伦之恋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.87,0:15:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}开玩笑啦开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.56,0:15:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那么 请问您要说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在这之前能先问一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当初为什么会想和香织说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明和香织一直做朋友是很辛苦的一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是那么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 那个 这和要谈的事有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天叫长谷同学来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是想告诉你我所知道的关于香织记忆的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学已经大概了解香织的情况了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也不知道为什么只有关于朋友的记忆会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是从什么时候开始的我还记得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小学六年级的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那孩子出了车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据目击者说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明是红灯 却横穿了马路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以才被车撞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在意识不明的状态下被抬进了医院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昏睡了好几天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.43,0:16:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然后意识恢复的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 妈妈 我说呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.31,0:16:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}他们是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什么是谁呀 不是你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.93,0:17:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}朋…友？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}据医生说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大脑没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.40,0:17:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然被车撞的时候 有轻微的脑震荡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但只有关于朋友的记忆会消失 有着其它的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其它原因？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对于朋友 可能有着精神上的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}精神上…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.88,0:17:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是啊 我完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织小时候朋友非常多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不管和谁都能马上成为好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}和朋友在一起的时候真的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织每天都和我说朋友的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也很喜欢听她说起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以 我不觉得她会跟朋友发生什么矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更不可能是装的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请问 发生事故的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织同学是一个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 听说是一个人横穿马路的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是一个周日傍晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}对了对了 她出门的时候说跟一个重要的朋友有约
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.39,0:18:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}重要的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.56,0:18:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 出门的时候笑得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是为什么会发生那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}让您回忆起悲伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.78,0:18:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 最难受的是香织
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}她每一次试着去想起朋友的时候都非常痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可能是香织自己在拒绝想起这些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 和你聊这么沉重的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里 能听您说这些真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然身为父母帮不了她感觉很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.05,0:19:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不过 光是有香织在我身边我就已经很幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算为过去的事情后悔 也解决不了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呐 你们牵过手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我… 我们只是朋友而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我差不多要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织该饿肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今后香织也拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能做到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织 这个拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}长谷同学能通过补考就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.56,0:19:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天呀 沙希和长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}午休的时候提起要复习功课
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.16,0:20:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沙希她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 昨天怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}香织 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.12,0:20:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.47,0:20:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学 早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}藤宫同学 早
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}现在在教室说话也没关系了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.27,0:20:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 早啊 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}昨天的补考能通过 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 也是勉勉强强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多亏了藤宫同学 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也要感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今早你在大家面前跟我打招呼 虽然让我有点惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:20:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}还有一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}回看日记时发现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}每周一的日记里都会写着一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你觉得是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.43,0:21:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}请再跟我做朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我说啊 长谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.78,0:21:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下周我也可以继续等着这句话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}当然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.45,0:21:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}关于她的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}虽然有了一知半解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但也仍然一头雾水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}说实话 对于藤宫同学的这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有时候也会觉得很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}尽管如此 只要能帮藤宫同学找回失去的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我还是会鼓起勇气 继续和藤宫同学做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}无论几次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.06,0:21:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都将持续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}「Ho」的朋友。「Hu-」的朋友。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
